title: while running in Colab - value error: unrecognized track method

labels.name: howtousedlc
labels.description: issue regarding the use of DeepLabCut

body:
Hi,

I've been using DLC on google colab. I trained a new set today and trying to test it out. But I got the following error while doing that on the analyze video step.
Colab version : 2.1.10.4

Can you help me solve this issue ?

Please place code inside this:
<videofile_path = ['/content/drive/My Drive/DLC/videos'] 
deeplabcut.analyze_videos(path_config_file,videofile_path, videotype='avi')>
